{"ID":"20240201213703-hdoz13u","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20240201213703-hdoz13u","title":"employee-performance","updated":"20240201213703"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213704-ygsoenh","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20240201213704-ygsoenh","updated":"20240201213704"}},{"ID":"20240201213705-9pua44t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213705-9pua44t","updated":"20240201213705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"title: 聊聊大厂的绩效考核"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"category: 技术文章精选集"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"tag:"}]},{"ID":"20240201213706-yzx3kwh","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"MarkerOffset":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213706-yzx3kwh","updated":"20240201213706"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213707-xnw3e58","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"MarkerOffset":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213707-xnw3e58","updated":"20240201213707"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213708-nd4fkcu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213708-nd4fkcu","updated":"20240201213708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"工作"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213709-ib3b5ln","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20240201213709-ib3b5ln","updated":"20240201213709"}},{"ID":"20240201213710-hse6d4h","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240201213710-hse6d4h","updated":"20240201213710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20240201213711-3f53r79","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213711-3f53r79","updated":"20240201213711"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"内容概览"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："}]},{"ID":"20240201213712-n4jw0n5","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213712-n4jw0n5","updated":"20240201213712"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213713-e7k1o6a","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213713-e7k1o6a","updated":"20240201213713"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213714-9bup9gw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213714-9bup9gw","updated":"20240201213714"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在大部分公司，绩效跟你的年终奖、职级晋升、薪水涨幅等等福利是直接相关的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213715-yy9ihrd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213715-yy9ihrd","updated":"20240201213715"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213716-239xdhx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213716-239xdhx","updated":"20240201213716"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你的上级、上上级对你的绩效拥有绝对的话语权，这是潜规则，放到任何公司都是。成年人的世界，没有绝对的公平，绩效考核尤为明显。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213717-cly64vz","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213717-cly64vz","updated":"20240201213717"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213718-641gpu3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213718-641gpu3","updated":"20240201213718"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提升绩效的打法："}]},{"ID":"20240201213719-mmkt6pb","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213719-mmkt6pb","updated":"20240201213719"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213720-qu65jjd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213720-qu65jjd","updated":"20240201213720"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213721-20vi6fw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213721-20vi6fw","updated":"20240201213721"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"短期打法：找出 1-2 件事，体现出你的独特价值（抓关键事件）。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213722-r2yd36z","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20240201213722-r2yd36z","updated":"20240201213722"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240201213723-6a1jl7x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213723-6a1jl7x","updated":"20240201213723"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"长期打法：通过一步步信任的建立，成为团队的核心人员或者是老板的心腹，具备不可替代性。"}]}]}]}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213724-u96k7bh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213724-u96k7bh","updated":"20240201213724"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"原文地址"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/D1s8p7z8Sp60c-ndGyh2yQ","TextMarkTextContent":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/D1s8p7z8Sp60c-ndGyh2yQ"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213725-9x6zdu3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213725-9x6zdu3","updated":"20240201213725"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在新公司度过了一个完整的 Q3 季度，被打了绩效，也给下属打了绩效，感慨颇深。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213726-xbwwrt5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213726-xbwwrt5","updated":"20240201213726"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"今天就好好聊聊"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"大厂打工人最最关心的「绩效考核」"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，谈谈它背后的逻辑以及潜规则，摸清楚了它，你在大厂这片丛林里才能更好的生存下去。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213727-72ykv42","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213727-72ykv42","updated":"20240201213727"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大厂的绩效到底有多重要？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213728-u4r36g0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213728-u4r36g0","updated":"20240201213728"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"先从公司角度，谈谈为什么需要绩效考核？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213729-e1j19ac","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213729-e1j19ac","updated":"20240201213729"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有一个著名的管理者言论，即：企业战略的上三路和下三路。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213730-ffczlkk","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240201213730-ffczlkk","updated":"20240201213730"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20240201213731-oo92pb9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213731-oo92pb9","updated":"20240201213731"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上三路是使命、愿景、价值观，下三路是组织、人才、KPI。下三路需要确保上三路能执行下去，否则便是空谈。那怎么才能达成呢？"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213732-b6b5sj2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213732-b6b5sj2","updated":"20240201213732"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"马老板在湖畔大学的课堂上，对底下众多 CEO 学员说，“只能靠 KPI。没有 KPI，一切都是空话，组织和公司是不会进步的”。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213733-f6r3px0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213733-f6r3px0","updated":"20240201213733"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以，KPI 一般是用来承接企业战略的。身处大厂的打工者们，也能深深感受到：每个季度的 KPI 是如何从大 Boss、到 Boss、再到基层，一层层拆解下来的，最终让所有人朝着一个方向行动，这便是 KPI 对于公司的意义。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213734-l988dcl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213734-l988dcl","updated":"20240201213734"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然鹅，并非每个员工都会站在 CEO 的高度去理解 KPI 的价值，大家更关注的是 KPI 对于我个人来说到底有什么意义？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213735-h51mqdh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213735-h51mqdh","updated":"20240201213735"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在互联网大厂，每家公司都会设定一套绩效考核体系，字节用的是 OKR，阿里用的是 KPI，通常都是「271」 制度，即："}]},{"ID":"20240201213736-3g2quoo","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240201213736-3g2quoo","updated":"20240201213736"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20240201213737-ye12r26","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213737-ye12r26","updated":"20240201213737"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"20% 的比例是 A+ 和 A，对应明星员工。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213738-m5y49ap","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213738-m5y49ap","updated":"20240201213738"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"70% 的比例是 B，对应普通员工。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213739-s7g1lh2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213739-s7g1lh2","updated":"20240201213739"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"10% 的比例是 C 和 C-，对应需要绩效改进或者淘汰的员工。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213740-y2139at","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213740-y2139at","updated":"20240201213740"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有了三六九等，然后才有了利益分配。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213741-y4isqs4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213741-y4isqs4","updated":"20240201213741"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"在大厂，绩效结果跟奖金、晋升、薪水涨幅、股票授予是直接相关的。在内卷的今天，甚至可以直接划上等号。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213742-jz5u0wp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213742-jz5u0wp","updated":"20240201213742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"绩效好的员工，奖金必然多，一年可能调薪两次，晋升答辩时能 PK 掉绩效一般的人，职级低的人甚至可以晋升免试。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213743-g7nj6xe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213743-g7nj6xe","updated":"20240201213743"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"而绩效差的人，有可能一年白干，甚至走人（大厂的末尾淘汰是不成文的规定）。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213744-76ycdr9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213744-76ycdr9","updated":"20240201213744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总之，你能想到的直接利益都和「绩效」息息相关。所以，在大厂这片高手众多的丛林里，多琢磨下绩效背后的逻辑，既是生存之道，更是一技之长。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213745-x7mwg75","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213745-x7mwg75","updated":"20240201213745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你是怎么看待绩效的？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213746-sadivz2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213746-sadivz2","updated":"20240201213746"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"凡是用来考核人的规则，大部分人在潜意识里都想去突破它，而不是被束缚。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213747-d0njml6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213747-d0njml6","updated":"20240201213747"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"至少在我刚工作的前几年，看着身边有些同事因为背个 C 黯然离开的时候，觉得绩效考核就是一个冷血的管理工具。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213748-ks8fay4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213748-ks8fay4","updated":"20240201213748"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"尤其遇到自己看不上的领导时，对于他给我打的绩效，其实也是很不屑的。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213749-ypg1ol3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213749-ypg1ol3","updated":"20240201213749"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"到今天，实在见过太多的反面案例了，自己也踩过一些坑，逐渐认识到：当初的想法除了让自己心里爽一点，好像起不到任何作用，甚至会让我的工作方式变形。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213750-3njsm4y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213750-3njsm4y","updated":"20240201213750"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当思维方式变了，也就改变了我对绩效的态度，至少有两点我认为是打工人需要看清的。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213751-eijli7r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213751-eijli7r","updated":"20240201213751"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"第一，你的上级、上上级对你的绩效拥有绝对的话语权，这是潜规则，放到任何公司都是。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213752-bwwm6g3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213752-bwwm6g3","updated":"20240201213752"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"大家可以去看看身边发展特别好的人，除了有很强的个人能力以外，几乎都是善于利用规则，而不是去挑战规则的人。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213753-n6y5xad","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213753-n6y5xad","updated":"20240201213753"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当然，我并不是说你要一味地去跪舔你的领导，而是表达：工作中不要站在领导的对立面去做对抗，如果领导做法很过分，要么直接沟通去影响他，要么选择离开。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213754-ikh88bq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213754-ikh88bq","updated":"20240201213754"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"第二，成年人的世界，没有绝对的公平，绩效考核尤为明显。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213755-p6zvkbk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213755-p6zvkbk","updated":"20240201213755"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我所待过的团队，绩效考核还是相对公平的，虽然也存在受照顾的情况，但都是个例。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213756-91gdwas","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213756-91gdwas","updated":"20240201213756"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外就是，技术岗的绩效考核不同于销售或者运营岗，很容易指标化。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213757-d5ml77y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213757-d5ml77y","updated":"20240201213757"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"需求吞吐量、BUG 数、线上事故... 的确有一大堆研发效能指标，但这些指标在绩效考核时是否会被参考？具体又该如何分配比重？本身就是一个扯不清楚的难题。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213758-eln7x27","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213758-eln7x27","updated":"20240201213758"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最终决定你绩效结果的还是你领导的主观判断。你所见到的 360 环评，以及弄一些指标排序，这些都只是将绩效结果合理化的一种方式，并非关键所在。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213759-jvsw5rt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213759-jvsw5rt","updated":"20240201213759"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"因此，多琢磨如何去影响你的领导？站在他的视角去审视他在绩效考核时到底关注哪些核心点？这才是至关重要的。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213760-z2bpbzj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213760-z2bpbzj","updated":"20240201213760"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上面讲了一堆潜规则，是不是意味着绩效考核是可以投机取巧，完全不看工作业绩呢，当然不是。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213761-7wcbtzz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213761-7wcbtzz","updated":"20240201213761"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“你的努力不一定会被看见”、“你的努力应该有的放矢”，大家先记住这两条。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213762-zcmsd4z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213762-zcmsd4z","updated":"20240201213762"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我再展开聊聊，大家最最关心的 A 和 C，它们背后的逻辑。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213763-jpansum","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213763-jpansum","updated":"20240201213763"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"绩效被打 A 和 C 的逻辑是什么？"}]},{"ID":"20240201213764-f6c2ydk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213764-f6c2ydk","updated":"20240201213764"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“铆足了劲拿不到 A，一不留神居然拿了个 C”，这是绝大多数打工人最真实的职场现状。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213765-a62l0ss","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213765-a62l0ss","updated":"20240201213765"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A 和 C 属于绩效的两个极端，背后的逻辑类似，反着理解即可，下面我详细分析下 C。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213766-1v4mz2l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213766-1v4mz2l","updated":"20240201213766"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"先从我身边人的情况说起，我所看到的案例绝大多数都属于：绩效被打了 C，完全没有任何预感，主管跟他沟通结果时，还是一脸懵逼，“为什么会给我打 C？一定是黑我呀！”。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213767-sbt1551","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213767-sbt1551","updated":"20240201213767"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"前阵子听公司一位大佬分享，用他的话说，这种人就是没有「角色认知」，他不知道他所处的角色和职级该做好哪些事？做成什么样才算「做好了」？被打 C 后自然觉得是在背锅。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213768-cd69eu5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213768-cd69eu5","updated":"20240201213768"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"所以，务必确保你对于当前角色是认知到位的，这样才称得上进入了「工作状态」，否则你的一次松懈，一段不太好的表现，很可能导致 C 落在你的头上，岗位越高，摔得越重。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213769-pd3sefh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213769-pd3sefh","updated":"20240201213769"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有了角色认知，再说下对绩效的认知。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213770-xonujwp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213770-xonujwp","updated":"20240201213770"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第一，团队很优秀，是不是不用背 C？不是！大厂的 C 都是强制分配的，再优秀的团队也会有 C。所以团队越厉害，竞争越惨烈。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213771-zrcelw6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213771-zrcelw6","updated":"20240201213771"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二，完成了 KPI，没有工作失误，是不是就万事大吉，不用背 C？不是，绩效是相对的，你必须清楚你在团队所处的位置，你在老板眼中的排序，慢慢练出这种嗅觉。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213772-7q32srb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213772-7q32srb","updated":"20240201213772"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"懂了上面这些道理，很自然就能知道打 C 的逻辑，C 会集中在两类人上："}]},{"ID":"20240201213773-e7hnr4p","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20240201213773-e7hnr4p","updated":"20240201213773"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20240201213774-gbgvtym","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213774-gbgvtym","updated":"20240201213774"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、工作表现称不上角色要求的人。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213775-gglbhs1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213775-gglbhs1","updated":"20240201213775"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、在老板眼里排序靠后，就算离开，对团队影响也很小的人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20240201213776-99znxfg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213776-99znxfg","updated":"20240201213776"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"要规避 C，有两种打法。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213777-el26cak","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213777-el26cak","updated":"20240201213777"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第 1 种是短期打法：抓关键事件，能不能找出 1-2 件事，体现出你的独特价值（比如本身影响力很大的项目，或者是领导最重视的事），相当于让你的排序有了最基本的保障。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213778-6ix5mh0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213778-6ix5mh0","updated":"20240201213778"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这种打法，你不能等到评价时再去改变，一定是在前期就抓住机会，承担起最有挑战的任务，然后全力以赴，做好了拿 A，不弄砸也不至于背 C，就怕静水潜流，躺平了去工作。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213779-8ys808z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213779-8ys808z","updated":"20240201213779"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第 2 种是长期打法：通过一步步信任的建立，成为团队的核心人员或者是老板的心腹，具备不可替代性。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213780-h0pqddy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213780-h0pqddy","updated":"20240201213780"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"上面两种打法都是大的思路，还有很多锦上添花的技巧，比如：加强主动汇报（抹平领导的信息差）、让关键干系人给你点赞（能影响到你领导做出绩效决策的人）。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213781-r5kxg9b","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213781-r5kxg9b","updated":"20240201213781"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"写在最后"}]},{"ID":"20240201213782-hqavm98","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213782-hqavm98","updated":"20240201213782"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有人的地方就有江湖，有江湖就一定有规则，大厂平面看似平静，其实在绩效考核、晋升等利益点面前，都是一场厮杀。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213783-88i4o05","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213783-88i4o05","updated":"20240201213783"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当大家攻山头的能力都很强时，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"到底做成什么样才算做好了？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当你弄清楚了这个玄机，职场也就看透了。"}]},{"ID":"20240201213784-xkj4wig","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240201213784-xkj4wig","updated":"20240201213784"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果这篇文章让你有一点启发，来个点赞和在看呀！我是武哥，我们下期见！"}]},{"ID":"20240201213785-sft8mki","Type":"NodeHTMLBlock","Data":"\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003c!-- @include: @article-footer.snippet.md --\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e","HtmlBlockType":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240201213785-sft8mki","updated":"20240201213785"}}]}